Devops Roadmap -- Done

Devops -- Devops is a process of improving the application delivery by ensuring
that there is a proper Automation , quality, continuos monitoring/observability,
 continuos Testing in place

Automation -- lines/piece of code without manual process

Scaling -- the application should be available when there is a high availabilty
without any issues.

Devops is important to improve the process of delivary [Automation and Fast].
